(1, 'SM MARINE SERVICE | Marine Automation,Navigation and Communication Equipment supplier. ', 'SM Marine Service have the pleasure to introduce with our company name SM Marine Services  for your kind reference and future necessary action.We are biggest stockiest for all kind marine  Navigation and Communication Equipment, Automation,Navigation,Hydraulic Pump and motor,Com pressure,Fire detection system etc .  We are one point marine supplier solutions for all your vessels requirements. \r\nOur company provides the highest quality services.', 'Navigation, Automation and Communication Equipment ,Electronics Systems,Hydraulic Pump, Navigation Electronics like Gyro Compass, Autopilot, GPS, AIS, Echo Sounder, Weather Fax, Speed Log, VDR / SVDR, Navtex, Wind meter, SatCom Antenna, Main and Auxiliary Engine and their parts, Diesel Generator Sets and many more related equipment.\r\n', 'uploads/SiteImages/smarinlogo.jpg', 'uploads/SiteImages/WhatsApp_Image_2023-08-17_at_8_42_38_PM.jpeg', 'Mohiddin Market (2nd floor), Abdul Barek Road, North Pahartali, Chittagong, Bangladesh.', 'WhatsApp : +88 01818929292', 'sohelbhuiyan1213@gmail.com  sohel.rana21@yahoo.com  ', 'Thank you very much for visiting our web site.We have the pleasure to introduce with our company name SM Marine Services for your kind reference and future necessary action.We are biggest stockiest for all kind marine Automation,Navigation,Hydraulic Pump and motor,Com pressure,Fire detection system etc . We are one point marine supplier solutions for all your vessels requirements. Our company provides the highest quality services. We are a trusted service provider over a decade with our efforts and our client’s satisfaction.We listen carefully and understand the needs of our clients. We have been committed to setting the highest standards for quality and client service within the given period of time whatever your vessels needs, we can help.', 'SM Marine Service have the pleasure to introduce with our company name SM Marine Services  for your kind reference and future necessary action.We are biggest stockiest for all kind marine  Navigation and Communication Equipment, Automation,Navigation,Hydraulic Pump and motor,Com pressure,Fire detection system etc .  We are one point marine supplier solutions for all your vessels requirements. \r\nOur company provides the highest quality services.\r\n', 'S M Marine Service respond to the customer calls within the shortest possible time ever. We work 24×7 and response time is within 30 mints as we value your time.\r\n\r\nFrom the Service front, we do not restrict ourselves from offering our services at various other ports. S M Marine Service go that extra mile to fulfill our commitment to the customers, and services can be arranged to anywhere in Bangladesh Ports, and we are having monopoly availability of stock in various Marine Electronics.', 'SM MARINE SERVICE is located at Chittagong, Pahartali , Mohiddin Market in Bangladesh. The company was established and incorporated in the year May 2004 by a professional who is well versed with Best experience in the field of Marine Navigation, Automation Electronics & Communication Equipment of ship.\r\n\r\nWe deal in used Marine Navigation, Automation, Communication & Electronics Systems as well as and Instrumentation. Main and Auxiliary Engine, Diesel Generator Sets and all types of other Marine Machinery. We are amongst the major buyers of equipment acquired from the vessels recycled at Bangladesh. If you are a vessel owner / fleet manager or a dealer of these equipment you can buy quality second hand equipment from us at a very reasonable cost which we can delivery anywhere across the globe.\r\n\r\nWe will regularly update this site with the details of our vast range of stock of New and  used Automation goods,  Bridgeroom Navigation Electronics like Gyro Compass, Autopilot, GPS, AIS, Echo Sounder, Weather Fax, Speed Log, VDR / SVDR, Navtex, Wind meter, SatCom Antenna, Main and Auxiliary Engine and their parts, Diesel Generator Sets and many more related equipment.', 'uploads/SiteImages/home_valueadd.jpg', 'uploads/SiteImages/voyage-data-recorder-vdr.jpg');
