(191, 10, 0, 'Rivertrace Engineering Smart Cell 15ppm Bilge Alarm, SmartCell', 'uploads/PostImages/SMART_CELL.jpg', ' Rivertrace Engineering Smart Cell 15ppm Bilge Alarm, SmartCell\r\n\r\nModel 	         SmartCell\r\nApplication 	15PPM OIL CONTENT MONITOR\r\nType 	         Wired\r\nBrand 	         Rivertrace Engineering\r\n\r\nThe “SmartCell” oil content monitor meets the requirements of MEPC 107 (49) for monitoring of 3 oil types: Fuel, Diesel and Emulsions. By utilizing the “SmartCell” Detector Array Technology, the OCM analyses all three oil types simultaneously without the need for re-calibration. A manual cell clean devise is included as standard to easily.\r\n\r\n\r\nSmart Cell Bilge Alarm Detector Array Technology, developed by Rivertrac, the OCM analyses all three oil types (HFO, Diesel and Emulsions) simultaneously without the need for re-calibration.\r\n\r\nA manual cell cleaning device is included as standard to easily enable routine maintenance. Optical cell fouling is recognised as a leading cause of monitor malfunction or incorrect reading. By simple operation of the manual cleaning device, the Smart Cell remains in optimum operating condition. Replacement calibrated measuring cells can be purchased for easy change over on board the vessel and calibration verification kits enable the crew to demonstarte the monitor is within factory calibration to PSC Surveyors.\r\n\r\nThe Smart Cell Bilge Alarm is readily available as a 5ppm version if required. It can also be tailor made for Hazardous Environments (Zone 1 & 2) as an Exd system with Auto Clean, all enclosed in an explosion proof cabinet. ', 0, 0, '12:50', 'February 23, 2022', 'February 23', 1, 1, 1, '', '', '', '', '2021-10-31 12:39:49'),
