(6, 'About Us', 1, 1, '<p> Thank you very much for visiting our web site.We have the pleasure to introduce with our company name SM Marine Services for your kind reference and future necessary action.We are biggest stockiest for all kind marine Automation,Navigation,Hydraulic Pump and motor,Com pressure,Fire detection system etc . We are one point marine supplier solutions for all your vessels requirements. Our company provides the highest quality services. We are a trusted service provider over a decade with our efforts and our client’s satisfaction.We listen carefully and understand the needs of our clients. We have been committed to setting the highest standards for quality and client service within the given period of time whatever your vessels needs, we can help. </p>'),
(8, 'Services', 2, 1, '<p>We are a quality provider for sales &amp; service of Marine Electronics, Communication, Navigational &amp; Automation equipment as well as Engine items.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe repair Marine Electronics, Communication, Navigational &amp; Automation equipment .We will always try to repair a product where possible before suggesting that it should be replaced and we carry an extensive range of spare parts for a wide variety of marine electronic and navigation equipment. We can often repair equipment regarded as obsolete by the manufacturer &ndash; extending the life of your equipment and offering you savings.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur multi-skilled engineers can complete any kind of tasks on-board, whether related to Navigation and Communication products or Connectivity Solutions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe build our relationship with customers to fulfill their expressed needs and expectations, to be a long term associate and to be regarded as a friend, consultant and active partner in their business. We support the products and technology to the satisfaction of the customers with the correct attitude.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a good reputation in the shipping market all over the world for quality services. We have a well-equipped workshop, where the latest technology instruments are used. Our reliable services have been recognized by the major Marine classified societies. For test and repair of ships we have well skilled engineer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
(11, 'Company Profile', 1, 1, '<p><strong>SM MARINE SERVICE</strong> is located at Chittagong, Pahartali , Mohiddin Market <strong>in Bangladesh</strong>. The company was established and incorporated in the year May 2004 by a professional who is well versed with Best experience in the field of Marine Navigation, Automation Electronics &amp; Communication Equipment of ship.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We deal in used Marine Navigation, Automation, Communication &amp; Electronics Systems as well as and Instrumentation. Main and Auxiliary Engine, Diesel Generator Sets and all types of other Marine Machinery. We are amongst the major buyers of equipment acquired from the vessels recycled at Bangladesh. If you are a vessel owner / fleet manager or a dealer of these equipment you can buy quality second hand equipment from us at a very reasonable cost which we can delivery anywhere across the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will regularly update this site with the details of our vast range of stock of used Bridgeroom Navigation Electronics like &nbsp;Gyro Compass, Autopilot, GPS, AIS, Echo Sounder, Weather Fax, Speed Log, VDR / SVDR, Navtex, Wind meter, SatCom Antenna, Main and Auxiliary Engine and their parts, Diesel Generator Sets and many more related equipment.</p>\r\n'),
(12, 'Quality', 1, 1, '<h2>Quality</h2>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are providing high quality services for Marine Navigational  Communication & Electronics, Systems and as well as Automation and Instrumentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>S M Marine Service never compromise on quality service and hence successfully achieved a high level of customer appreciation resulting in extending our services with long lasting relations.</p>\r\n'),
(13, 'Vision', 1, 1, '<h2>Vision</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;To make everyone comfortable with latest technologies available and to become one of the down to earth Integrator/ Solution Provider in this world&rsquo;&rsquo;</p>\r\n');
